{"tid":380454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過因為無錢 令你留下一啲唔想再面對既回憶","createTime":"2017-08-30T06:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T09:22:28.000Z","uid":14753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec00cc5801359c432e752b98d77e495f9e9d4642","tid":380454,"uid":14753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"由細到大都無零用錢 細個果陣都明白屋企環境唔好<br />\n中學都係晏就都係行返屋企食<br />\n所以1$都無<br />\n上到中學 唔識死走去溝女<br />\n第一年女朋友生日 唔敢問老豆老母拎錢買禮物 走去問堂家姐借 佢唔借 我夠膽死問阿麻借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢都無錢 都比左兩舊我<br />\n如是者 買完禮物 食飯 <br />\n因為當日係節日<br />\n成班同學約去打邊爐<br />\n我當然唔夠錢比 結果要問個同學借<br />\n我真係想搵lone捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個月之後岩岩好15歲 即刻見老麥<br />\n放學放假就返工 出糧即刻還錢比同學<br />\n同比返封利是阿麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到今時今日 我都覺得好難受 唔想再記起"},{"pid":"f1d45209be4aacf0bc8b406a0b586747abd89dc6","tid":380454,"uid":139700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:38:21.000Z","msg":"睇錯無綫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68242966790abf1f0ac527875e88cf23e3a6f76b","tid":380454,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"你再唔發奮就會變到我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fbde9fc93b9f95f27ce4205a995088be03658a","tid":380454,"uid":19948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"無錢仲買嘢俾女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb1341dfc882a153cfda6e0e39f64f58572b702","tid":380454,"uid":14753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:18:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錢仲買嘢俾女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一次同佢過生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0d24f30176241be3a5bb837ed75e88f013b223","tid":380454,"uid":14753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你再唔發奮就會變到我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打點解咁講<br />\n不過已經係11年前既事<br />\n因為無錢 畢業之後即刻做野 無hea過<br />\n因為呢個香港無錢真係乜都無得傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5962c85da9a5e092f9ae42a6e17278e5a7bda591","tid":380454,"uid":71726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"無錢唔夠膽溝女"}]}